  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>The Hotel Austria has a central location in Niederau and offers excellent value for money. This comfortable hotel has room types to suit everybody and a heated indoor pool to end the day in.</span></p>
<h2><span>Central location</span></h2>
<p><span>The Hotel Austria is great for convenience with a central location in <a data-udi="umb://document/3c1c4e119772493fa932ed5a06912edf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3c1c4e119772493fa932ed5a06912edf}" title="Niederau">Niederau</a>  </span><span>opposite</span><span> the Markbachjoch gondola. The ski school meets at the same place and the hotel has its own in-house ski hire shop for added convenience.</span></p>
<h2><span>Rooms and apartments</span></h2>
<p><span>Hotel Austria offers a range of rooms, each designed with comfort in mind. Whether you're looking a single room, a double, or a larger apartment for the whole family, you’ll find the rooms equipped with everything you need for a relaxing stay. All rooms have a balcony so you can enjoy views of the surrounding mountains.</span></p>
<h2><span>Comfort &amp; convenience</span></h2>
<p><span>The hotel has a lounge area with open fireplace to relax in after a day on the slopes. The hotel's heated indoor pool is a great place to unwind. The sauna and steam room are open Sunday to Friday to keep warm in.</span></p>]]></description>
